00:28:46.358 --> 00:28:47.319
Thanks.

00:28:47.319 --> 00:28:49.379
I thought you didn’t offer credit.

00:28:49.379 --> 00:28:51.489
It depends on who that customer is.

00:28:51.489 --> 00:28:55.514
He's been my customer for a very long long time.

00:28:55.514 --> 00:28:57.526
