00:29:36.009 --> 00:29:36.881
Um.

00:29:37.262 --> 00:29:40.769
If you like it, come and eat at our place anytime.

00:29:40.769 --> 00:29:42.664
We always have a full table of food.

00:29:42.664 --> 00:29:44.210
All your staff at the diner are welcome too.

00:29:44.210 --> 00:29:45.152
I don’t want to trouble you.

00:29:45.152 --> 00:29:46.281
Don’t worry about it.

